{"tid":1317491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係有需要整鐵馬？","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:58:37.000Z","uid":113716,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"05f0f21d805040ab63288f46f6a078bd9753af90","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4bd8b2ad6707ac764ca40de7b21be41b4acbcb","tid":1317491,"uid":230658,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:58:00.000Z","msg":"只可以講好過冇 <br />\n但作用不大 <br />\n易拆易過"},{"pid":"9a77cfc7e7a3740cd397d03cf01f66a90293ad0c","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:03:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"60fc6eb1784cd29c6033f1b4073e67dc90bffcbe","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:04:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6813c0342dab298710b67cb4887524ddd8440ab","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:04:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"42ff1c402e7056ec78083df51a4b01b2f2bd6252","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3361ded114f2bdb1ed9aa5a4739123033eb723fb","tid":1317491,"uid":81385,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"05f0f21d805040ab63288f46f6a078bd9753af90","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:09:52.000Z","msg":"今日見有雙層，有啲用<br />\n狗要界爛先要埋身<br />\n今次係人撤佢先咁快過防線，都用左成5分鐘，當然有用"},{"pid":"0619b14fd77d886c3d8490dcce19b6950691376b","tid":1317491,"uid":65342,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"巴打 睇直播答你<br />\n頭先攻個陣班狗要推開鐵框 <br />\n但佢第一時間唔拆/ 拆起馬要兩分鐘<br />\n搞到只可以每次兩三人過<br />\n你話要唔整鐵欄俾人直衝 ？"},{"pid":"06c0b08d04e957b0b95d580e2a9333eea8321d5e","tid":1317491,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"一定有需要<br />\n面對面對住衝埋黎，後面退唔切一定有手足被拉"},{"pid":"8c860691225ab7f1891eca5b5ce3bb6a6f88131f","tid":1317491,"uid":126317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"05f0f21d805040ab63288f46f6a078bd9753af90","tid":1317491,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:29:36.000Z","msg":"所以五年前既佔中，銅鑼灣佔區咪有人用鋼索威也囉⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個鐡馬只用幾條威也，已將怡和街前後兩段鐵馬陣鎖死<br />\n<br />\n平、實用、快，果晚見佢串幾個圈就搞掂，兩三分鐘就將兩個鐵馬緊緊串起，<br />\n<br />\n但要有工具威也鉗，普通野，五金舖常見<br />\n<br />\n當年見警方凌晨清場時，要個別警員用大剪鉗，花時間去每個鐵馬拆開"},{"pid":"1b8227b6494d1457af702200fdd53fe5a8da857c","tid":1317491,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f0bf2d2fa7a796093e0042cd46498a3b621828","tid":1317491,"uid":117251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:41:42.000Z","msg":"今日發夢有工程大叔教用幾條鐵絲加固，用鉗扭幾扭，會好硬淨，又難拆"},{"pid":"9a5f181597fa53f0cc1ea54bdf56bac3a617f480","tid":1317491,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f0bf2d2fa7a796093e0042cd46498a3b621828","tid":1317491,"uid":117251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:41:42.000Z","msg":"今日發夢有工程大叔教用幾條鐵絲加固，用鉗扭幾扭，會好硬淨，又難拆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:43:42.000Z","msg":"push ar"},{"pid":"015f85d2e0bdc9acec1e2b94c04917cc873dcb28","tid":1317491,"uid":43413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:43.000Z","msg":"發夢好似話驚有車衝人群"},{"pid":"ff9b0e0f4541b348b3450029160d15a31fc569c3","tid":1317491